      <scopecontent id="aspace_34dffd6840f7e516faf8e6ae3f819730">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This listing encompasses accessions of single manuscripts and small groups of manuscripts pertaining to Max Beerbohm. Materials acquired prior to January 1995 have been arranged in three series. <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref11">Series I, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Letters</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>, consists of letters by Max Beerbohm and is alphabetically arranged by recipient. <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref38">Series II, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Writings</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>, contains writings by Max Beerbohm and is arranged alphabetically by title. <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref56">Series III, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Artwork</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>, contains drawings and sketches by Max Beerbohm and is arranged alphabetically by title of work.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
